high_descs: Stay in the current spot, and face to the left where the microwave is.
Open the microwave and take out the bowl. Shut the door.
Take the bowl and go left, then right to find the fridge.
Open the fridge to put the bowl inside, then shut the door. Open the door and take the bowl out and shut the door.
Take the bowl to the left, and then right to face the white door.
Place the bowl on the brown shelf to the right.
anns.task_desc: Move a bowl from the microwave to a shelf.

high_descs: Begin walking over to the counter, then turn left and walk up to the microwave.
Open the microwave door and take out the glass bowl out of the microwave, then close the door.
Turn left and walk over to the black fridge.
Put the glass bowl in the fridge for a couple seconds to let it get cold, then take it out of the fridge and close the door.
Turn to your left and begin walking across the room, then hang a right and walk up to the wooden shelving unit in the corner of the room.
Put the chilled glass bowl in the middle of the top shelf of the wooden shelving unit.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled glass bowl on the wooden shelving unit.
